            <title>[SYNAPSE-797] Query parameters get dropped when we use Endpoint format as rest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-797</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The query parameters of the incoming request get dropped with a &apos;rest&apos; endpoint.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;address uri=&quot;http://localhost:6060&quot; format=&quot;rest&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/send&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
